org.polarsys.chess.core.profiles

Class CHESSProfileManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.polarsys.chess.core.profiles.CHESSProfileManager

  • public class CHESSProfileManager
extends java.lang.Object
    This class wraps the CHESS profile resource and is used for loading the profile and applying its stereotypes. It contains also a set of constants to identify a number of item, such as Design Views, subprofile names, stereotypes, ...
    Author:
    Alessandro Zovi
